text: Keshav Raj Pandey (Neapli: केशवराज पाण्डे) is a Nepalese politician and former member of the Bagmati Provincial Assembly. He had previous as Minister of Internal Affairs and Law and Minister for Physical Infrastructure Development of Bagmati Province. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Keshav Raj Pandey
